# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).


## [2.0.1]

### Changed

- `--stage` option made optional

### Added

- If no stage provided, user is prompted with an interactive selector


## [2.0.0]

### Added

- Plugins support added.

### Changed/Fixed

- Dependencies updated to latest versions.
- Better support for AWS CDK CLI (https://gitlab.com/vinm/vinm-cli/-/issues/2).
- Ability to run multiple pipelines in parallel (https://gitlab.com/vinm/vinm-cli/-/issues/1).
- Logs output improved.

### Removed

- Socket.io dependency removed.
- Vinm emitter port (--port option) removed.


## [1.1.3]

>  Plugins support still in preview

### Changed

- Bug fix - error when loading plugins from node_modules


## [1.1.2]

### Added

- Plugins support added (preview only)


## [1.1.1]

### Changed

- Bug fix "Assignment to constant variable."


## [1.1.0]

### Added

- Tasks/pipelines report summary after execution

### Changed

- Bug fix with --force option
